OL,5, A black hole in local authority budgets
OL,6, continues to grow, a BBC investigation 
OL,7, reveals, prompting fears some will not 
OL,8, be able to provide basic services.     
OL,10,FThe average council now faces a #33m   
OL,11,F($42m) predicted deficit by 2025-26 - a
OL,12,Frise of 60% from #20m two years ago.   
OL,14,FUnison said the situation meant some   
OL,15,Fcouncils would not be able to offer the
OL,16,F"legal minimum of care" next year.     
OL,18,FThe government said decisions on the   
OL,19,Ffunding beyond the next financial year 
OL,20,Fhad not yet been made.                 
